title: Grateful Dead - 1971-10-21-22 - Auditorium Theater in Chicago, I
description:
Grateful Dead
1971-10-21 & 10-22
Auditorium Theatre
Chicago, IL

Dave's Picks Vol. 3

Source: Official Dead.net CD's > EAC > TLH (flac level 8) > Helium Music Manager (tags)

EAC Logs and Hi Rez. Scans included

Limited to 12,000 individually numbered copies
Mastered to HDCD specs by Jeffrey Norman
Digipak made of 100% recycled and PCW materials
Release Date: August 1, 2012

Since NO LONGER AVAILABLE, I wanted those who missed the chance to get it have the opportunity to listen to this gem of Grateful Dead history.
